posting_body: ["Please text, or email because i can't answer unknown calls while working or helping family.", 'Available for one person.', "We can't have two renters.", 'Month to month with No long-term contract required, but feel free to stay long-term.', 'Private entrance and private everything furnished apartment with everything you need.', 'Rent price is $694 + $196 for all utilities (water, electricity, cable TV, WI-FI internet) per month.', 'Just pay the first month to move in.', 'Included are a furnished Kitchenet for cooking and refrigerating, plus furnished Living Room with TV & WI-FI, Bedroom stuff, a full Bathroom, and all utilities (water, electricity, cable TV, WI-FI internet)', 'This is a tenet-at-will agreement so you can move out whenever you want.', 'Most guests decide to stay long-term.', 'On four acres of private property with two other private apartments, and nature all around.', 'The private apartments are attached to a private residence house.', 'Everything is private.', 'Renters come and go privately, and are appreciated as people with lives to live.', '**PARTY FREE**NOISE FREE**ISSUE', 'FREE**ALCOHOL FREE**DRUG FREE**SMOKE', 'FREE**OVERNIGHT GUEST FREE (except for family)**', 'Just private and relaxing.', 'Available so contact us to see your apartment!']
